MH Tri VR is a fork-based project built on Dolphin Emulator and is licensed under the
GNU General Public License, version 2 or (at your option) any later version
(GPL-2.0-or-later), the same as Dolphin.

Full corresponding source for any distributed binary is the Dolphin fork:
  https://github.com/Matt-Wood-23/dolphin  (branch: mhtri-vr)

The complete GPL-2.0 text is included in that repository (COPYING). This repository
holds documentation and release packaging for the project.

MH Tri VR is an unofficial fan project. It is not affiliated with, authorized, or
endorsed by Nintendo, Capcom, or the Dolphin Emulator project. No game files are
distributed; you must supply your own legally-obtained copy of Monster Hunter Tri.
